entries.s_ff20b1f1: Yes, please reset my employment history.
entries.s_faf7c09a: Very well, it is done. You may continue your service to the almighty Jabba the Hutt where you last left off.
entries.s_f7565bbd: YES, I am sure. I want to continue my service.
entries.s_f3139d0: Very well. Return when you are available.
entries.s_ebce22a9: NO, wait. Let me think a moment longer.
entries.s_eac2e473: If I reset your history, you will be able to go back and assist Lord Jabba again as you have done in the past. But don't worry, you will be rewarded, and it will in no way reduce your standing in the eyes of Jabba the Hutt. Shall I reset your history?
entries.s_e3c4a3d5: No, do not reset my history. I will continue my service.
entries.s_e11b3d7c: Keep in mind that once I reset your history, it cannot be undone. Are you sure that you want me to reset your employment history?
entries.s_c7528c3b: I am sure you can imagine the turmoil it caused. Those on Jabba's payroll are no longer getting paid, and those in debt to him, were free of their obligations. Needless to say, the CZ droid responsible was... disciplined.
entries.s_c1ff278a: I must recompile all of the data that was lost. For that reason, I must ask you some questions.
entries.s_badb4859: Remember that once you decide to continue, you cannot change your mind. Are you sure that you want to continue your services to Jabba where you left off?
entries.s_b193a14c: Alright, but keep in mind that once I reset your history, it cannot be undone. Are you sure that you want me to reset your employment history?
entries.s_adccd297: Your services for Jabba have already been recorded. I have no need to speak to you.
entries.s_a76f22bf: What if I decide to reset my history?
entries.s_960270ff: Very well. But do not take long.
entries.s_93e226b7: NO, do not reset my history right now.
entries.s_866cf013: I see. What do you need me for?
entries.s_741d0966: If you choose to continue from where you left off, you will simply return to the person which last gave you a job. That person will then tell you how you may best serve Jabba. But remember that once you decide you cannot change your mind. Shall I reset your history?
entries.s_72907ccb: If I reset your history, you will be able to go back and assist Jabba again as you have done in the past. But don't worry, you will be rewarded again, and it will in no way reduce your standing in the eyes of Jabba himself. Do you want me to reset your history?
entries.s_710595f4: I've got to be going now.
entries.s_6e88ecc1: No, do not reset my history right now.
entries.s_6d63d30d: As you wish. Come back and speak to me again if you change your mind.
entries.s_630c8b2: Very well, it is done. You should speak to Reelo Baruk when you wish to serve his highness, Lord Jabba, again.
entries.s_5e8caf64: If you like, I can reset your employment history and you may serve Lord Jabba again. Otherwise, you can continue your service to him where you left off. Remember that once you decide, you cannot change your mind. Shall I reset your history?
entries.s_5cc1a230: It would seem that you have performed great services for Jabba in the past, and he has rewarded you well. However, if you wish, I can reset your employment history in our records. Do you want me to reset your history?
entries.s_555b76aa: As you wish. Return to me when you have made your decision.
entries.s_4fd35e09: YES, I am sure. Reset my employment history.
entries.s_3be84186: Yes, I do need to speak with you. I have questions that you need to answer.
entries.s_3ae9c534: You have not performed any services for his exaltedness, Jabba the Hutt. I do not need to speak to you.
entries.s_34f17e66: Due to an unfortunate incident caused by an irresponsible little droid, CZ-4, all of Lord Jabba's employment and accounting records were erased.
